reviews.review: Uh... What did I just watch?
Why can i not watch the movies

I thought Foodfight! and Norm of the North were bad, but this movie actually comes really close to be one of the worst movies of all time. Even though the animation is OK, the plot is confusing, the writing is really over the top, the characters are lame, the comedy is awful, the pop culture reference are way too many, and even the moral does nothing to support the movie. In fact can I even call it a movie!? I give credit to its cast including TJ Miller, Anna Farris and Patrick Stewart, but their talents are just wasted in this movie. And can't believe I have to say this, but this movie even had the balls to steal the plots from other movies like The LEGO Movie, Wreck-It Ralph and Inside Out. I mean...really!? Sony cancelled The Popeye Movie for this!? F*** YOU SONY YOU BASTARDS!!!

This was really funny, but I think kids older than 12/13 would find it really cheesy and not as good as they thought. I personally quite enjoyed it, James Corden is really funny. Recommended for kids under 12 and adults.
WTF??? I mean what the actual f*ck?!

Not amazing but certainly not worthy of this dismal rating. Actually brings humor and creates a clever concept. Everyone being different but the same and everyone expecting you to conform to the system when some people simply cannot or see how phony it is to live life at face value.

this movie is packed with fun. the first part of the movie has 5 poop jokes. i personally think that they shouldn't have backed off on them. a sequel would be fantastic. i love how the characters are totally original and cool. the story is amazing and there are no frame drops in the film. my favorite character is the meh parents. there mono tone of voice never gets old. you should watch it over and over again.
My 6 and 4 year old girls liked it.

Besides the trolls that say this is a masterpiece and some teens and kids, i can't picture anyone saying this is a great movie, everything this movie makes it's wrong. Every choice is non-sensical and stupid, every character is cruel and mean-spirited, every joke is flat and annoying, every app promoted in this movie is pandering the audience, every emotional and "profound" scene it's stupid and puts sad music to treat the audience like stupid, every piece of animation is done badly, everything this movie presents has already done a million times better. It is one of the worst animated movies i've ever seen and it's not even suitable for children, it's a terrible kids film and a failure of animation. Avoid it as much as you can. Do not be fooled, because it's not enjoyable bad, this is painfully bad.
